On Wednesday the committee resolved to call Brown and the Eskom board to explain the recent reappointment of Eskom CEO Brian Molefe which has caused public outrage. This was at the request of DA spokesperson on public enterprises Natasha Mazzone. Lynne Brown and Eskom board told to appear in Parliament on FridayRantho said in a statement that Brown had been summoned to court over the appointment of Molefe and therefore we are unable to discuss the matter as it is subjudice and as the committee we are unable to do proper oversight as planned. The committee said it was disappointed at the latest developments at Eskom.TMG Digital/BusinessLIVE